BBNaija Season 6 ‘Shine Ya Eye’ housemate Maria has claimed every man she comes across wants to sleep with her. The bi-racial reality TV star, in a post said, her DM is choked up with messages from different men expressing how much they want her. She, however, noted she was unavailable because she has a man in her life. “I’m on every nigga hit list, check my DM. Problem is I gat a man,” Maria wrote. Reacting to Maria’s declaration, social media users had a lot to say. - Advertisement - While some praised her, others chided her. symplychi_oma said: “Nobody needs irrelevant information in 2022.” broda_henry wrote: “Heaven should be your goal this 2022, not all this worldly shit talks!” futballpunter stated: “Maria rest in the mighty name of Jesus.”   Doctors said I wouldn’t make it past 2020, says Uche Ogbodo     Mbaka gifts ‘Akanchawa’ singer Gozie new Lexus     How Nollywood can go global, by BBN Leo Dasilva   nellynells__ asked : “Are you on Gods list ? Eh?” abimbolaicey said: “Are you an assassin madam.. na wa for who no dey hit list oooo.” bigbaby548 wrote: “Lol.. thank God she know say na hit list..” ella_abua stated: “This one still dey talk hit list not marriage list sef.” kvng_lheo asked: “Are you on heaven’s list?” kingin_kezie said: “You are not the only one , Women are natural gift from God to us Men . There’s nothing special it’s just the way of life.” dromomurewa_ wrote: “Every man? Definitely not me! I’d rather go to Peckers.” pinzle_ceo stated: “Just say the streets is entering your eye.” vinexcel_david said: “This one is Almost 40 and she here talking about the damn hit list.” lucyrose67124 wrote: “You’re indirectly saying those men aren’t seeing wife potential in you aside hitting? Stop!”